///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
@11506 = ~Serrated Bone Blade +3~
@11507 = ~Emanating a faint blue aura, this gigantic weapon is a serrated two-handed sword made of bone. It will occasionally strike with a shocking force of cold, chilling the victim to the bone.

STATISTICS:

